ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:12:04.000Z","msg":"所以咪無乜所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，來回最多三千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"係無乜所謂，但就係成班人為左幾舊水屌曬人老母又叫人便宜仔又話先達狗請人排隊，笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6a63b9fd6faf16717d2afa627ae06285513436","tid":2286322,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"去1010 用visa $7500 以上平$550 啦"},{"pid":"e130a8ab54bc3a53f14d96270257c1f7a469ce75","tid":2286322,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6a63b9fd6faf16717d2afa627ae06285513436","tid":2286322,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"去1010 用visa $7500 以上平$550 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:17:01.000Z","msg":"用Club like積分加Mox bank5%回饋，平千一添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc60cf45002e5ffe7f32222d2d87a035ffde2c1","tid":2286322,"uid":21732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:17:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-01/20/38813.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thinkhk.com%2Farticle%2F2020-01%2F20%2F38813.html&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BKEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=93608d89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thinkhk.com/article/2020-01/20/38813.html</a><br />\n<br />\n「炒樓只是個開始，炒風無限延伸，演唱會飛、紀念鈔、iPhone、波鞋、手袋、玩具⋯<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n進階版的有疫苗、咪錶位以及康文署體育館的場紙，小市民只想輕輕鬆鬆打波減壓都要捱炒價，還真是可憐！<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n最令人哭笑不得的還有廚師腸，2018年尾時，美國廚師牌雞肉腸因為母公司破產而面臨停產，因為承載着港人回憶，網上一度將炒價推至400元一包，直至香港代理於三個月後，宣佈以同樣配方再度生產後，炒風才得以終結。<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n不論是樓、是口罩、還是廚師腸，這些都是實體經濟下所產生的投機行為，雖不違法，但若然不守住道德底線，經濟壓榨行為可能會變得愈來愈過火，甚至產生惡性循環，彷彿擁有市場觸覺便有「錢途」或是有利可圖，<strong><span class=\"red\">人人都只希望賺快錢，哪裡還有心力想去拼、敢去闖？至於底線在哪裡</span></strong>，還是要靠自己定義吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自私撚條底線就係唔影響到自己就okay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47318c09eacc105e95de9bc32c54c2b8ecb27513","tid":2286322,"uid":14739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6a63b9fd6faf16717d2afa627ae06285513436","tid":2286322,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"去1010 用visa $7500 以上平$550 啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:17:42.000Z","msg":"hkbn 屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cf057677c523455373faffcf91c096b6781be9","tid":2286322,"uid":159313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:18:37.000Z","msg":"連登仔早排先笑完先達沒落等執柒<br />\n轉頭又喪家狗咁去俾人撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b7c1afcbe028bbcd3b403c824288ae9a82847b","tid":2286322,"uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f267379a1cefe2ee3dd88b1d287a75a4c510385","tid":2286322,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"驚係因為班人無錢找卡數？<br />\n全新Apple 跌都係平手/跌幾舊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"卡數都無咁快找啦<br />\n月頭先比錢"},{"pid":"fe1d4dd557bcced2b00fd27f5d4569506dff57f5","tid":2286322,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84b7c1afcbe028bbcd3b403c824288ae9a82847b","tid":2286322,"uid":12705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f267379a1cefe2ee3dd88b1d287a75a4c510385","tid":2286322,"uid":18444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:05:06.000Z","msg":"驚係因為班人無錢找卡數？<br />\n全新Apple 跌都係平手/跌幾舊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:23:35.000Z","msg":"卡數都無咁快找啦<br />\n月頭先比錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"驚drop to zero ar <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04f439f18261efbd728ab33c1